WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:03.600 --> 00:00:30.720
Will I start now, Gavin?

00:00:30.720 --> 00:00:33.960
…5 of May 1970.

00:00:33.960 --> 00:00:46.560
Actually, that also came
very spontaneously

00:00:46.560 --> 00:00:54.080
because the atmosphere
was not ready as yet,

00:00:54.080 --> 00:01:08.400
and the evolutionary last jump
of human beings into the unconscious

00:01:08.400 --> 00:01:13.680
was organized and arranged
and thought of.

00:01:13.680 --> 00:01:22.800
But the time to do that
was depending on many factors.

00:01:24.480 --> 00:01:36.000
The first factor, the foremost factor
was, how far human beings

00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:40.400
have been able to keep them
in the central path.

00:01:41.840 --> 00:01:45.840
That was the most important.

00:01:45.840 --> 00:01:50.320
Because as far as the development
of the intelligence was concerned,

00:01:50.320 --> 00:01:57.920
or say the ego and superego
was concerned, the process was over.

00:01:57.920 --> 00:02:00.240
It was just fixed.

00:02:00.240 --> 00:02:04.960
This happened the time I was born.

00:02:04.960 --> 00:02:09.360
And when this body came on this earth,
it came with all its symbols.

00:02:11.040 --> 00:02:13.680
That's why so many people saw
this big chakra coming.

00:02:13.680 --> 00:02:15.360
It exists in the Sahasrara.

00:02:16.800 --> 00:02:21.440
And they saw also the cross coming.

00:02:21.440 --> 00:02:39.680
They saw also the Mooladhara symbol,
'swastika'.

00:02:39.680 --> 00:02:45.520
But the process of activating
those symbols

00:02:45.520 --> 00:02:48.640
started much earlier
than the last one.

00:02:48.640 --> 00:02:55.200
This happened on the 5th of May, 1970.

00:02:55.200 --> 00:02:59.520
In my own lifetime,
apart from what happened earlier

00:02:59.520 --> 00:03:07.760
in this lifetime of mine,
the first chakra of Mooladhara

00:03:07.760 --> 00:03:20.577
was activated in the year 1950 or so.

00:03:20.577 --> 00:03:28.031
When I was in Shimla, it happened.

00:03:28.031 --> 00:03:29.440
The Mooladhara chakra has got,
you know, swastika at emblem.

00:03:29.440 --> 00:03:37.680
The swastika completely started
revolving in the sky.

00:03:37.680 --> 00:03:48.560
And the chakra formed
a line of the sky.

00:03:48.560 --> 00:03:50.480
It opened up.

00:03:50.480 --> 00:03:56.560
And through that,
the symbol came out.

00:03:56.560 --> 00:04:02.960
And the symbol also then sort of
emitted light.

00:04:02.960 --> 00:04:06.480
And that also then opened the sky
even higher.

00:04:06.480 --> 00:04:11.360
That's how the first chakra opened up.

00:04:11.360 --> 00:04:13.920
I mean, to describe it is very
difficult,

00:04:13.920 --> 00:04:17.920
because it's a thing that moves
like the smoke, you see, that moves.

00:04:19.360 --> 00:04:26.240
And so to describe it in its whole
appearance is difficult.

00:04:26.240 --> 00:04:31.280
Because you see the movement
of the smoke here: it is so mobile.

00:04:31.280 --> 00:04:34.720
In the same way, the chakra is also
a very mobile thing.

00:04:34.720 --> 00:04:38.000
It is a living, mobile thing.

00:04:38.000 --> 00:04:41.360
It changes its form,
becomes bigger, smaller,

00:04:41.360 --> 00:04:49.200
expands, revolves, stops.

00:04:49.200 --> 00:04:55.120
Now the swastika was the first symbol.

00:04:55.120 --> 00:04:59.040
And it's the most important one.

00:04:59.040 --> 00:05:04.400
And that started in 1950,
as I told you, when I was in Shimla.

00:05:04.400 --> 00:05:07.760
When it happened, after that,
one by one,

00:05:07.760 --> 00:05:13.760
the center started opening out
in the sky.

00:05:13.760 --> 00:05:18.500
But not there, later on
and later on and later on,

00:05:18.500 --> 00:05:23.280
till it came to the Sahasrara.

00:05:23.280 --> 00:05:25.360
I won't be able to give you
the complete accounts

00:05:25.360 --> 00:05:34.480
on what date and how it happened,
but it's various stages.

00:05:34.480 --> 00:05:41.033
As it is, in the evolutionary stages,
you have crossed all these chakras

00:05:41.033 --> 00:05:42.240
within yourself.

00:05:42.240 --> 00:05:47.338
For example, you have choked,
you have controlled

00:05:47.338 --> 00:05:48.920
this Vishuddhi chakra,
you have raised your head fully.

00:05:48.920 --> 00:05:53.680
In the primitive people, if you find,
they have got this one bending like this.

00:05:53.680 --> 00:05:55.760
But you have got it all right.

00:05:55.760 --> 00:06:00.400
And then your ego also developed
quite a lot.

00:06:00.400 --> 00:06:04.720
And you are just ready for this Agnya,

00:06:04.720 --> 00:06:09.680
when Christ came in
and He also opened this one for you.

00:06:11.360 --> 00:06:18.080
But in the human awareness,
now you must understand

00:06:18.080 --> 00:06:23.360
that human awareness
is what you are today.

00:06:23.360 --> 00:06:25.920
That is what you should call
as human awareness.

00:06:25.920 --> 00:06:29.680
There is no limit to it,
because the instrument is the same.

00:06:29.680 --> 00:06:34.240
For example, today you can play
one raga with five notes;

00:06:34.240 --> 00:06:37.040
notes permutations and combinations,
you know.

00:06:37.040 --> 00:06:40.240
But tomorrow, you may learn
to do it even better.

00:06:40.240 --> 00:06:42.800
And day after tomorrow, even better.

00:06:42.800 --> 00:06:46.000
But it is all linked to one instrument.

00:06:46.000 --> 00:06:53.120
So the human instrument is the same,
only your awareness increases.

00:06:53.120 --> 00:06:56.800
So from my birth only,
the awareness started increasing.

00:06:56.800 --> 00:07:01.680
But especially this Mooladhara's
opening, perhaps,

00:07:01.680 --> 00:07:04.480
must be coinciding with the 50s.

00:07:04.480 --> 00:07:08.880
I don't know when it started actually,
but it should coincide about that time.

00:07:08.880 --> 00:07:12.800
Because that's the time,
the Mooladhara's opening

00:07:12.800 --> 00:07:17.040
broke the materialism of us—
materialism.

00:07:17.040 --> 00:07:22.160
Because of materialism, you see,
people lost their vision of the reality.

00:07:22.720 --> 00:07:25.280
They never thought of the beyond.

00:07:25.280 --> 00:07:30.640
And the human beings, sort of,
got materialized into the material.

00:07:30.640 --> 00:07:33.120
So, at that time it was necessary
to break

00:07:33.120 --> 00:07:37.280
and to bring to their awareness
the knowledge

00:07:37.280 --> 00:07:39.280
that the matter is not real.

00:07:39.280 --> 00:07:42.080
There is something of the beyond,
one has to go beyond.

00:07:42.080 --> 00:07:45.280
And that happened about 1950 or 49.

00:07:48.880 --> 00:07:51.760
But that's the time
when I worked in Simla.

00:07:51.760 --> 00:07:54.480
It happened for the first time.

00:07:54.480 --> 00:08:01.200
I should say it would be 50
or a little earlier, a little bit earlier.

00:08:01.200 --> 00:08:08.240
And after that, you see,
this new awareness came into human beings.

00:08:08.240 --> 00:08:12.160
That you are the same person,
but you are open to new dimensions.

00:08:12.160 --> 00:08:14.960
And this was one of the new dimensions
started.

00:08:14.960 --> 00:08:22.240
That matter broke its form,
broke its bondage.

00:08:25.920 --> 00:08:34.720
And this first chakra,
means the matter chakra,

00:08:34.720 --> 00:08:37.840
is made from the Mother Earth.

00:08:37.840 --> 00:08:40.480
And Ganesha is this.

00:08:40.480 --> 00:08:43.680
It is through his power it broke.

00:08:43.680 --> 00:08:47.680
The bondage of matter
on human beings broke.

00:08:47.680 --> 00:08:51.760
First, there was a struggle
between the matter and the Spirit,

00:08:52.480 --> 00:08:57.920
but a point came where the bondage
lifted itself in awareness,

00:08:57.920 --> 00:09:01.360
in instinctive awareness.

00:09:01.360 --> 00:09:06.480
Awareness is through thinking,
in the thoughts, in the inspired thoughts.

00:09:06.480 --> 00:09:09.280
People felt that we are under
the bondage of the matter.

00:09:09.280 --> 00:09:11.120
So the first thing started.

00:09:11.120 --> 00:09:14.000
Gradually, one after another,
if you see,

00:09:14.000 --> 00:09:18.000
it's clearly in those 50 years,
suddenly the creativity started.

00:09:18.000 --> 00:09:20.880
It triggered because of
the Swadisthana,

00:09:21.520 --> 00:09:24.960
people became very creative,
in a sense, coloured now.

00:09:24.960 --> 00:09:28.400
If you remember in London,
say, before 1950,

00:09:28.400 --> 00:09:32.080
people used to wear only a very odd black.

00:09:32.080 --> 00:09:34.720
And they would not, I mean,
even smile at people.

00:09:34.720 --> 00:09:38.400
They were so grey.
And everything was so grey.

00:09:38.400 --> 00:09:41.120
And nobody believed in any colour.

00:09:41.120 --> 00:09:44.160
Even Americans, they were very grey
people before that.

00:09:44.160 --> 00:09:48.500
But then, the colour started coming up
and people started believing in colours.

00:09:48.500 --> 00:09:50.720
A lot of colours started flowing
all over the world.

00:09:50.720 --> 00:09:55.040
People believed in colours.
And they became to wear colours.

00:09:55.040 --> 00:09:59.040
But awareness came when
the Swadishthana Chakra broke.

00:09:59.040 --> 00:10:02.400
Otherwise, you know how it was
everywhere,

00:10:02.400 --> 00:10:06.000
they didn't believe in any colour.

00:10:06.000 --> 00:10:10.880
And even they started painting
with more colourful things.

00:10:10.880 --> 00:10:16.400
At that time, abstraction of art
was much more prominent also.

00:10:16.400 --> 00:10:20.240
About that time should be—
of course, it started breaking much earlier.

00:10:20.240 --> 00:10:22.240
But it really broke about that time

00:10:22.240 --> 00:10:27.040
that people wholly started displaying
abstract art after 1960.

00:10:27.040 --> 00:10:29.520
Before that, it was sort of,
everybody used to laugh at it

00:10:29.520 --> 00:10:32.400
and say, you know,
Picasso was the one.

00:10:32.400 --> 00:10:34.320
But Picasso also didn't go
to that extent.

00:10:34.320 --> 00:10:38.080
But later on, I think,
the lines broke

00:10:38.080 --> 00:10:43.750
and the colour started flowing
and people started believing in colours.

00:10:43.750 --> 00:10:49.600
It was an abstraction of matter.
People started going to that side of it.

00:10:49.600 --> 00:10:58.400
After the Swadishthana Chakra,
the Nabhi Chakra started opening.

00:10:58.400 --> 00:11:01.920
The Nabhi Chakra problem was
that people started feeling

00:11:01.920 --> 00:11:05.280
that there's nothing in the plastic.

00:11:05.280 --> 00:11:07.680
Nothing in these things
that you are possessing.

00:11:07.680 --> 00:11:13.755
But it is the Lakshmi part of it
that matter is a thing

00:11:13.755 --> 00:11:20.000
that is for its aesthetic
and not for its value in the market.

00:11:20.000 --> 00:11:24.400
So people started thinking
about the Lakshmi part of it,

00:11:24.400 --> 00:11:32.880
that how we can take something
that is expensive but is beautiful.

00:11:32.880 --> 00:11:37.040
It is like the plastic and all that
really came up with Swadishthana.

00:11:37.040 --> 00:11:39.920
It started breaking down.

00:11:39.920 --> 00:11:42.800
It is here once upon a time
plastic was regarded as a strength.

00:11:42.800 --> 00:11:44.880
And then it broke down, you see.

00:11:44.880 --> 00:11:48.560
The awareness recently had passed
so quickly from one to another.

00:11:48.560 --> 00:11:51.440
It has never happened before
in that short time.

00:11:51.440 --> 00:11:54.880
If you see it in the 50 years of time,
it happened like that.

00:11:54.880 --> 00:11:58.320
So they started taking
to the Lakshmi side of the matter,

00:11:58.320 --> 00:12:04.720
that it should be decorating,
it should be joy-giving.

00:12:04.720 --> 00:12:09.120
And so then all these would be
more awareness towards the antique also

00:12:09.120 --> 00:12:12.800
developed, that people said,
"What's happening with plastic?"

00:12:12.800 --> 00:12:14.720
This awareness came in.

00:12:14.720 --> 00:12:15.840
Then came the Heart Chakra.

00:12:15.840 --> 00:12:18.960
And with the Heart Chakra,
people started thinking

00:12:18.960 --> 00:12:21.040
about the pollution part of it and all this,

00:12:21.040 --> 00:12:24.400
that was affecting the security
of human beings.

00:12:24.400 --> 00:12:25.680
They were so aware!

00:12:25.680 --> 00:12:27.440
I mean, nobody was aware of it.

00:12:30.960 --> 00:12:32.400
People became suddenly aware of it

00:12:32.400 --> 00:12:34.800
because it was people making more control

00:12:34.800 --> 00:12:38.080
that maybe their existence
will be endangered,

00:12:38.080 --> 00:12:39.840
sort of thing came up.

00:12:39.840 --> 00:12:45.840
And that's how people became very aware
of the pollution and things then.

00:12:45.840 --> 00:12:48.715
And with the sense of security only,
at that time,

00:12:48.715 --> 00:12:53.200
with the atomic bomb,
that atomic bomb came in.

00:12:53.200 --> 00:12:56.560
It came as really
as a protective measure for them.

00:12:56.560 --> 00:13:01.520
But then it is a rational thing,
because that really frightened everyone.

00:13:03.520 --> 00:13:05.760
You see, the German
that was using this stuff

00:13:05.760 --> 00:13:07.040
started frightening you.

00:13:07.040 --> 00:13:10.640
And you said, "Now, if you try to use
this again,

00:13:10.640 --> 00:13:12.480
it's going to destroy all of us".

00:13:12.480 --> 00:13:18.640
And that's how, you see,
we jumped into another awareness,

00:13:19.360 --> 00:13:28.640
where people started feeling,
"This world, what is it we've got?

00:13:28.640 --> 00:13:32.320
We have done one atomic bomb,
we've done this, we have done that.

00:13:32.320 --> 00:13:34.720
And what have we achieved?
Where are we?"

00:13:34.720 --> 00:13:37.600
Sort of things, you started
thinking about.

00:13:37.600 --> 00:13:41.995
It's such, the science and everything
that we have done now.

00:13:41.995 --> 00:13:42.720
It's not the one that we were seeking.

00:13:42.720 --> 00:13:44.720
There's something beyond.

00:13:44.720 --> 00:13:50.320
And this became a very, very strong
feeling in the West.

00:13:50.320 --> 00:13:56.720
And after, I think, 1960,
great souls started coming.

00:14:01.120 --> 00:14:07.280
From 60 onwards,
very, very great souls started coming.

00:14:07.280 --> 00:14:11.760
Because they thought that,
"Well, the time has come now

00:14:11.760 --> 00:14:14.560
for us to come down and help".

00:14:14.560 --> 00:14:20.000
But still there are so many of them
awaiting.

00:14:20.000 --> 00:14:25.920
Now, from 1960 to, say, 1970,
ten-year time, was the most crucial time.

00:14:25.920 --> 00:14:35.680
And the 60 to 70 time was the time
when seekers started becoming conscious

00:14:35.680 --> 00:14:51.214
about their own Realization.

00:14:51.214 --> 00:14:51.280
60 to 70, the seeking became
a sort of a real mass of great people.

00:14:51.280 --> 00:14:54.080
And they were just so restless
that they didn't know what to do,

00:14:54.080 --> 00:14:54.640
where to seek,

00:14:54.640 --> 00:14:58.720
and they were just breaking their heads
from 60 to 70.

00:14:58.720 --> 00:15:02.560
At 70, it happened.

00:15:02.560 --> 00:15:07.120
Now, as you all know,
that it is a living process,

00:15:07.120 --> 00:15:08.880
like a tree growing.

00:15:08.880 --> 00:15:12.560
And the tree, when it grows,
it doesn't go according to its planning,

00:15:12.560 --> 00:15:14.800
but according to its own time.

00:15:14.800 --> 00:15:20.000
But there is, of course, a season.
And the season comes in.

00:15:20.000 --> 00:15:26.800
But in the case of Sahaja Yoga,
the whole process is sahaj.

00:15:26.800 --> 00:15:30.240
But the whole continuous process of God

00:15:30.240 --> 00:15:35.840
is not based at all on the seasons
that He would create,

00:15:35.840 --> 00:15:40.480
but the seasons that you would create.

00:15:40.480 --> 00:15:44.320
It's a different touch,
that the season is to be created also

00:15:44.320 --> 00:15:48.640
by the seeker.

00:15:48.640 --> 00:15:51.920
So, it is what happens
in the evolutionary stages.

00:15:51.920 --> 00:15:54.640
A person reaches a certain stage,
one person,

00:15:54.640 --> 00:15:57.280
and then he creates
a kind of a season.

00:15:57.280 --> 00:15:58.240
Then the people come up.

00:15:58.240 --> 00:16:02.240
Then he reaches a certain point.
He creates another kind of a season,

00:16:02.240 --> 00:16:03.840
and then people come up.
It happens like that.

00:16:07.360 --> 00:16:10.080
I never knew that it would happen
that early,

00:16:10.080 --> 00:16:15.600
that I would be forced
to attain of that kind.

00:16:15.600 --> 00:16:19.840
And it just happened,
because I saw something terrible happening.

00:16:19.840 --> 00:16:22.480
I was among some people,
which I will tell you later on

00:16:23.120 --> 00:16:24.960
about the place where I was.

00:16:24.960 --> 00:16:28.720
The place is known as Nargol,
where I was with many other people.

00:16:28.720 --> 00:16:33.120
And there was a satanic person
who was doing satanic rules.

00:16:35.040 --> 00:16:36.541
And I could see, and I was unhappy.

00:16:36.541 --> 00:16:39.200
And I just felt at that time
that, "The time has come now".

00:16:39.200 --> 00:16:43.680
Because once it is expressed,
then people will become aware.

00:16:43.680 --> 00:16:50.240
And that was the time
when I just pushed my Kundalini up.

00:16:50.240 --> 00:16:59.760
So, once the Kundalini came up,
I see the Sahasrara of the Virata.

00:16:59.760 --> 00:17:03.511
And I saw the Kundalini of the Virata.

00:17:03.511 --> 00:17:06.480
That was of mine,
but how I saw it, I must tell you.

00:17:06.480 --> 00:17:13.266
I saw it from the side,
and I saw it in a slanting way.

00:17:13.266 --> 00:17:13.440
In a slanting way.

00:17:13.440 --> 00:17:22.800
I saw it in all angles,
the Kundalini was.

00:17:22.800 --> 00:17:25.280
And it opened out like a 'thak,
thak, thak, thak'.

00:17:25.280 --> 00:17:28.480
I saw it opening up like that,
going up, going up.

00:17:28.480 --> 00:17:31.440
And I saw it in all angles coming
before Me,

00:17:31.440 --> 00:17:33.831
so that I could know
where was the problem.

00:17:33.831 --> 00:17:37.280
Sort of, I took out myself to see it,
how it worked.

00:17:37.280 --> 00:17:40.156
And there was this whole process
in that Kundalini

00:17:40.156 --> 00:17:44.160
and it was in different colours,
you know all the different colours

00:17:44.160 --> 00:17:47.755
there are if you heat it up.

00:17:47.755 --> 00:17:53.596
Like if you have the iron
being heated up in the furnace,

00:17:53.596 --> 00:17:54.800
the colour was like that.

00:17:54.800 --> 00:17:58.160
It was red, and then another colour,
and another colour, and another colour.

00:17:58.800 --> 00:18:02.480
One after another,
the colour was coming.

00:18:02.480 --> 00:18:06.400
And I saw it coming up,
bubbling, like that.

00:18:06.400 --> 00:18:09.920
And the thing opened out
like a telescope.

00:18:09.920 --> 00:18:14.240
And then I saw, of course,
the Agnya.

00:18:14.240 --> 00:18:19.920
And Agnya was a narrow place,
no doubt, but still, it came into it.

00:18:19.920 --> 00:18:22.480
And then I saw the Sahasrara.

00:18:22.480 --> 00:18:28.960
And Sahasrara was like a huge,
big lotus, very huge, big lotus.

00:18:28.960 --> 00:18:30.800
But, you see, you can see with two eyes:

00:18:30.800 --> 00:18:33.520
if you see as God,
then you really see the whole.

00:18:33.520 --> 00:18:37.280
But as a human being,
I saw a lotus like this, so big as that.

00:18:38.960 --> 00:18:40.880
So big only, not more than that.

00:18:40.880 --> 00:18:44.320
I think, perhaps in your brain,
it's not so much big.

00:18:44.320 --> 00:18:46.320
And in my brain also
must be so much big.

00:18:46.320 --> 00:18:49.440
But if you see as a big person,
then you see your own big brain.

00:18:49.440 --> 00:18:52.960
But when you see as a small person,
you see that little brain of yours.

00:18:54.800 --> 00:19:01.440
And it was all, to Me,
what should you say, pulsating.

00:19:01.440 --> 00:19:07.120
And in the lower portion of the
Sahasrara was a reddish colour.

00:19:07.120 --> 00:19:10.240
And all the colours were there.

00:19:10.240 --> 00:19:14.880
But I think the violet was not on top.
Violet was on the fringes.

00:19:14.880 --> 00:19:19.120
But ending up into crystal colour,
absolutely white crystal colour.

00:19:19.120 --> 00:19:27.200
And the two sides of the ego
and super-ego just fell like that.

00:19:27.200 --> 00:19:31.600
And it opened out, opened out like that.

00:19:31.600 --> 00:19:38.000
And inside was the yellow of the Agnya,
I saw, very clearly, golden yellow.

00:19:38.000 --> 00:19:47.586
And inside the yellow was this small,
small little substance, also clearly,

00:19:47.586 --> 00:19:47.600
it opened out.

00:19:47.600 --> 00:19:50.320
And the Sahasrara opened out like that.

00:19:50.320 --> 00:19:58.560
And the Kundalini started pouring in,
constantly with heart and then it filled up.

00:19:58.560 --> 00:20:02.320
It was very beautiful feeling.

00:20:03.040 --> 00:20:09.200
And then I felt a torrential rain,
completely coming on earth, completely.

00:20:09.200 --> 00:20:10.880
That's the Grace I was feeling.

00:20:10.880 --> 00:20:18.150
Like the rain of…
but it's very smooth and very silent,

00:20:18.150 --> 00:20:21.520
an effect suddenly coming down
on the earth.

00:20:21.520 --> 00:20:25.440
And I felt the whole earth
was completely filled,

00:20:25.440 --> 00:20:29.120
completely filled with that Grace,
completely drenched,

00:20:29.120 --> 00:20:39.920
and there was nothing left of it,
like absolutely dissolved, every part of earth.

00:20:39.920 --> 00:20:42.597
And then I knew the time has come.

00:20:42.597 --> 00:20:42.640
But in the awareness, I said,
"Get out now".

00:20:42.640 --> 00:20:46.240
You now can feel the collective
awareness.

00:20:46.240 --> 00:20:50.320
I knew it was satanic.

00:20:55.120 --> 00:21:06.800
And that was the fifth day of May.

00:21:06.800 --> 00:21:12.880
I should say,
it was done near the sea shore.

00:21:12.880 --> 00:21:16.320
And for two nights I had not slept.

00:21:16.320 --> 00:21:21.520
I was just staying there, near the sea.

00:21:21.520 --> 00:21:23.280
I didn't eat anything.

00:21:23.280 --> 00:21:27.280
I should get into the pool,
come back, again sit down.

00:21:27.280 --> 00:21:32.960
And just, I was just thinking
how to cleanse the world,

00:21:32.960 --> 00:21:35.360
or universe, or whatever you may call it.

00:21:35.360 --> 00:21:39.040
That this should happen.
And it worked.

00:21:39.040 --> 00:21:41.680
Because, you know, I reached the point
where I felt that,

00:21:41.680 --> 00:21:45.837
"It is important now.
There's no more to be fulfilled.

00:21:45.837 --> 00:21:48.640
It has to be done".
And it happened.

00:21:48.640 --> 00:21:53.040
And when it happened,
I felt the whole thing, sort of…

00:21:53.040 --> 00:22:04.720
It is something like an ocean of bliss
filling up every bit of it.

00:22:04.720 --> 00:22:06.640
Everywhere now it acts and it works.

00:22:06.640 --> 00:22:10.640
And that's why, when you get
your Realization,

00:22:10.640 --> 00:22:16.080
you get a move—how it works out,
how it sprouts, how it helps you,

00:22:16.080 --> 00:22:21.120
and how it acts on you,
without even your knowledge.

00:22:21.120 --> 00:22:23.520
And then, you can also see it sometimes.

00:22:23.520 --> 00:22:26.320
I mean, I don't know,
I can see it all the time.

00:22:26.320 --> 00:22:28.560
But in India, it is much more,

00:22:28.560 --> 00:22:40.000
that if you see in the sky,
you see them just like, like commas,

00:22:40.000 --> 00:22:41.582
like small commas.

00:22:41.582 --> 00:22:41.617
You see them glittering in the air.

00:22:41.617 --> 00:22:41.672
It's just the atmosphere itself
that's like half commas.

00:22:41.672 --> 00:22:44.400
You can see them in the air.

00:22:48.480 --> 00:22:49.680
And that's what it is.

00:22:49.680 --> 00:22:54.720
Because that Grace which came on this
earth, broke into these small commas

00:22:54.720 --> 00:22:57.840
and spread out everywhere.
And that acts.

00:22:57.840 --> 00:23:01.360
And that's how now you know the reality.

00:23:01.360 --> 00:23:02.320
This is what it is.

00:23:02.320 --> 00:23:06.000
And tonight I'm going to tell you
about reality, what this reality is.

00:23:06.000 --> 00:23:10.960
Because so far, whatever you have known,
has been all unreal.

00:23:10.960 --> 00:23:13.760
Now you know what this reality is.

00:23:13.760 --> 00:23:16.240
And this reality is very different
from that.

00:23:16.240 --> 00:23:18.080
I mean, the whole thing is changed now.

00:23:18.080 --> 00:23:19.120
The whole drama is over.

00:23:19.120 --> 00:23:20.800
Now you know it was a drama.

00:23:20.800 --> 00:23:22.480
So now you have come to another world.

00:23:22.480 --> 00:23:24.000
And this is another thing.

00:23:24.000 --> 00:23:27.360
And that is why today
is a very important day.

00:23:27.360 --> 00:23:29.680
That it is important for you

00:23:29.680 --> 00:23:35.840
that God in his grace and compassion
has done this.

00:23:35.840 --> 00:23:37.920
And it's more important for you

00:23:37.920 --> 00:23:40.000
that now you can dissolve into it,

00:23:40.000 --> 00:23:47.840
to be assimilated into that,
to be one with that,

00:23:47.840 --> 00:23:51.120
to be that instead of thinking
of the past.

00:23:51.120 --> 00:23:53.920
That was all a myth. It's over.

00:23:53.920 --> 00:23:57.040
Now the myth is over.
Your eyes are open.

00:23:57.040 --> 00:24:00.240
So, forget about your past,
and forget what you have done.

00:24:00.240 --> 00:24:04.480
Even what your so-called sins
you have committed is all over now,

00:24:04.480 --> 00:24:05.440
finished.

00:24:05.440 --> 00:24:08.880
There's nothing to do with it,
it's all over.

00:24:08.880 --> 00:24:10.160
Come to the present

00:24:10.160 --> 00:24:16.880
which comes in this beautiful world
of collective consciousness,

00:24:16.880 --> 00:24:23.040
where you realize that you are a part
and parcel of that great Being.

00:24:23.040 --> 00:24:24.560
And you are not alone.

00:24:24.560 --> 00:24:26.720
And you are to be cured,
and you are to be all right,

00:24:26.720 --> 00:24:30.080
and you are to be perfectly in harmony
with the great Being.

00:24:30.080 --> 00:24:35.040
If the great Being has told you
to do that.

00:24:35.040 --> 00:24:38.320
So, you don't have to bother much
about things that happened.

00:24:38.320 --> 00:24:40.480
Because now you have come into it.

00:24:40.480 --> 00:24:46.800
But only thing is, you have to go
deeper and deeper and deeper

00:24:46.800 --> 00:24:47.840
into yourself

00:24:47.840 --> 00:24:57.760
and deny all that is superficial
and become that what you are.

00:24:57.760 --> 00:25:08.024
It is a force that should love,
really it should love

00:25:08.024 --> 00:25:08.048
and should melt in that.

00:25:08.048 --> 00:25:10.000
It's meant to do that.
It should dissolve itself.

00:25:10.000 --> 00:25:11.680
It's a tremendous force.

00:25:11.680 --> 00:25:17.280
It is not a receding force as we say
or a very sort of a compromising force.

00:25:17.280 --> 00:25:20.320
It is not an aggressive force also.

00:25:20.320 --> 00:25:25.360
But it is the force,
all others are useless things.

00:25:25.360 --> 00:25:26.480
It is the light.

00:25:26.480 --> 00:25:29.920
The light has no end
and the darkness has to go.

00:25:29.920 --> 00:25:33.120
Because there is no light,
that's why there is darkness.

00:25:33.120 --> 00:25:36.400
So when the light comes in,
it doesn't mean it is aggressing

00:25:36.400 --> 00:25:37.600
the darkness.

00:25:37.600 --> 00:25:39.040
No, it is not.

00:25:39.040 --> 00:25:42.160
Because the light is there,
the darkness has disappeared.

00:25:42.160 --> 00:25:45.920
That's why you have to face this fact
that you are the light.

00:25:45.920 --> 00:25:48.080
And when you see,
you should be the light.

00:25:48.080 --> 00:25:51.520
And you should not be afraid
as to how to please others,

00:25:51.520 --> 00:25:54.880
how to be kind to others,
nothing else as such is needed.

00:25:54.880 --> 00:25:56.960
You are speaking with authority itself.

00:25:56.960 --> 00:25:58.560
It's the greatest kindness.

00:25:58.560 --> 00:26:02.560
Because then you tell them,
that this is the truth.

00:26:02.560 --> 00:26:06.720
Like a child afraid of a snake
lying on the ground.

00:26:06.720 --> 00:26:08.720
And you should tell the child,
"No, this is not a snake.

00:26:08.720 --> 00:26:14.320
Just see this. It is not a snake.
It's just an ordinary rope".

00:26:14.320 --> 00:26:17.760
Is there anything wrong
in such an assertion?

00:26:17.760 --> 00:26:22.960
So a Sahaja Yogi has
a very direct responsibility.

00:26:22.960 --> 00:26:26.960
Unless and until you have that kind
of a personality,

00:26:26.960 --> 00:26:30.160
you cannot emit or reflect that.

00:26:30.160 --> 00:26:33.591
You may receive it,
but that reflection has to come.

00:26:33.591 --> 00:26:35.680
You have to give it.

00:26:35.680 --> 00:26:41.275
And so I would like you today,
that you dissolve within yourself.

00:26:41.275 --> 00:26:47.200
That not only you receive it,
but you emit it with confidence,

00:26:47.200 --> 00:26:50.000
not with aggression,
but with confidence.

00:26:50.000 --> 00:26:54.320
There is nothing to bend before
the people who are in the myth.

00:26:54.320 --> 00:26:56.560
If you have known the reality,
it is better you tell them, fast.

00:26:56.560 --> 00:27:03.680
Before you sit with them and try
to keep them down, sit there.

00:27:03.680 --> 00:27:05.520
No, you have to tell them,
"No, no, no, no.

00:27:05.520 --> 00:27:08.640
This is the thing we found out.
It's the fact. It's the truth.

00:27:08.640 --> 00:27:13.596
We have felt, it is so.
There is God and He looks after us.

00:27:13.596 --> 00:27:16.640
And it is He who manages everything.
He does everything.

00:27:16.640 --> 00:27:21.197
You are just living with a myth!"

00:27:21.197 --> 00:27:24.560
It definitely helps, your confidence.

00:27:24.560 --> 00:27:26.136
And that's what today I bless you with,

00:27:26.136 --> 00:27:26.156
that you get to God.

00:27:26.156 --> 00:27:35.200
But the whole universe gets
its confidence in righteousness,

00:27:35.200 --> 00:27:40.800
in virtue, and in divine providence.

00:27:40.800 --> 00:27:49.440
Complete confidence into that.

00:27:49.440 --> 00:27:52.480
Now we are going to have the puja.

00:27:52.480 --> 00:27:54.880
Those who have come for the first time,

00:27:54.880 --> 00:27:59.329
I would like one or two of them
to come down

00:27:59.329 --> 00:27:59.360
if they believe in Sahaja Yoga.

00:27:59.360 --> 00:28:04.440
Now, it may be very difficult
for people to come up

00:28:04.440 --> 00:28:09.920
and to understand why to have puja.

00:28:09.920 --> 00:28:17.680
Now, you see, these small little things
that you see are your own symbols.

00:28:18.400 --> 00:28:19.200
All right?

00:28:22.480 --> 00:28:26.400
But what you do is a symbol
of your love.

00:28:26.400 --> 00:28:28.160
Those symbols are very important

00:28:28.160 --> 00:28:31.120
because the Unconscious understands
the symbols

00:28:31.120 --> 00:28:32.960
and gives you also symbols.

00:28:32.960 --> 00:28:35.760
So when you do this puja, I tell you,

00:28:35.760 --> 00:28:44.160
what happens: the Unconscious sees it
and is there.

00:28:44.160 --> 00:28:46.400
It's a very simple thing
if you understand

00:28:46.400 --> 00:28:50.800
that puja has nothing to do
with a particular flower as such.

00:28:50.800 --> 00:28:54.400
But it's very subtle feeling
that is inside,

00:28:54.400 --> 00:28:57.840
that when you are giving the flower
to the Unconscious,

00:28:57.840 --> 00:29:02.400
it accepts and it emits more love.

00:29:02.400 --> 00:29:11.840
And through that,
people have come out very fast.

00:29:11.840 --> 00:29:21.280
It's a very fast-moving Kundalini,
when it is drenched in the puja like this,

00:29:21.280 --> 00:29:23.520
it moves very fast, it clears you.

00:29:23.520 --> 00:29:26.720
And you really need that to go to God.

00:29:26.720 --> 00:29:31.280
That's how you feel this puja's
vibrations then you'll be sorted out.

00:29:31.280 --> 00:29:34.560
So, don't be sceptical about it.

00:29:34.560 --> 00:29:37.040
Only, keep yourself open.

00:29:37.040 --> 00:29:40.000
Because to undergo a puja
is not easy for Me,

00:29:40.000 --> 00:29:41.680
because I get tremendous vibrations.

00:29:41.680 --> 00:29:44.560
I need at least 10,000 people
to absorb that.

00:29:44.560 --> 00:29:47.120
And with very few people, it's difficult.

00:29:47.120 --> 00:29:49.520
So, very difficult for Me, you know,

00:29:49.520 --> 00:29:52.880
and I get… then I have to see God
who takes them back.

00:29:52.880 --> 00:29:57.120
But the more you absorb,
the more you are going to help.

00:29:57.120 --> 00:29:58.631
And I will be helped too.

00:29:58.631 --> 00:30:01.360
You see, I can't live without you
and you can't live without Me.

00:30:01.360 --> 00:30:03.120
It's a mutual problem.

00:30:03.120 --> 00:30:08.480
So, it's a fact. I tell you that.

00:30:08.480 --> 00:30:19.200
And I have to surrender
to your humanness that you absorb.

00:30:19.200 --> 00:30:24.560
Because your absorption
is going to reduce the obstacle.

00:30:24.560 --> 00:30:25.600
This is what it is.

00:30:25.600 --> 00:30:29.200
It's absolutely mutual,
as the rapport of that.

00:30:29.200 --> 00:30:33.840
So, there is nothing that I am giving
to you or you are giving.

00:30:33.840 --> 00:30:38.560
Because as I said, that you give Me
something, I give you something.

00:30:38.560 --> 00:30:42.145
Now, supposing if somebody makes you
stand with all these things on the head.

00:30:42.145 --> 00:30:45.520
Supposing, now say it like this.
You'll be tired.

00:30:45.520 --> 00:30:48.880
In the same way, when you give it to Me,
you see, the load that I have,

00:30:48.880 --> 00:30:51.120
you must take also.

00:30:51.120 --> 00:30:55.760
It's a simple given thing business.
And it is nothing more than that.

00:30:55.760 --> 00:30:58.880
But it's beautiful
because when you get it,

00:30:58.880 --> 00:31:04.720
when you get it in such a supreme state,
it's a beautiful state

00:31:04.720 --> 00:31:06.960
that you can remember this state.

00:31:06.960 --> 00:31:09.200
Because that remembrance
and that memory

00:31:09.200 --> 00:31:13.145
will always bring you again back to it.

