who removes all the hurdle

00:39:31.600 --> 00:39:36.400
and he is the one
who gives us wisdom.

00:39:36.400 --> 00:39:41.600
"Please grant us wisdom
and remove all the hurdle

00:39:41.600 --> 00:39:43.760
